{"tid":2385983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《南早》指中聯辦增加百人大軍 熟悉社交媒體打網戰","createTime":"2021-01-29T10:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T06:08:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb9155455b1b71fffddb21341c9f4adba7722ea","tid":2385983,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:04:07.000Z","msg":"日前有指中聯辦進行「海嘯式」人事更替。《南華早報》今日再引述內地消息指，北京早在去年已計劃進行人事更替，惟因應本港疫情爆發才暫緩，而今次來港的200人大軍當中，有大約100人是淨增長 。<br />\n<br />\n《南早》引述的內地消息指，北京去年已計劃安排約200名幹部加入中聯辦，「當中有100位是淨新增的人員」（The net increase was about 100），惟因應本港疫情爆發（because of the pandemic and the circumstances in Hong Kong），令有關改動暫緩至今。<br />\n<br />\n該消息人士續指，北京看中有關人士熟悉網上社交媒體、期望這批人能在港「重新開始 （ready to start fresh）」。<br />\n<br />\n該報另引述消息指，是次中聯辦增加人手編制，是因為中聯辦將「肩負更多工作」（Beijing had given more responsibilities），包括落實「由愛國者統治」（Ruled by patriots）、協助港府抗疫工作及協助港府與香港青年修補關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210129/TLRUPW7QUJDZ7EMK5KIYXKHRUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210129%2FTLRUPW7QUJDZ7EMK5KIYXKHRUA%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=fc8ad6eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210129%2FTLRUPW7QUJDZ7EMK5KIYXKHRUA%2F&h=dec4173d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210129/TLRUPW7QUJDZ7EMK5KIYXKHRUA/</a>"},{"pid":"eef8139accfef4753755e7330c56d393777e86b1","tid":2385983,"uid":19126,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"收皮啦食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232deb7bbbdf3260eb78b19032f70523aa3c9b05","tid":2385983,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo